## WebAssembly.Instance.prototype.exports getter

The [`WebAssembly.Instance.prototype.exports`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebAssembly/Instance/exports) property returns an object containing all the exported functions, constants, and memories from the WebAssembly module instance.

### Distorted Behavior

This distortion throws if functions exported from a WebAssembly instance are called with `eval`.
